AUCTION BID
----------

   Auction houses are located in each major city of all non-backwater planets.
Items that are auctioned can be bid on for the first 24 hours of being there.
After that all bids are closed and the highest bidder can go to any auction
house to pick up the object. If no one bids on it, the original owner can go
to an auction house and cancel the auction. If the highest bidder doesn't pick
up the object within 6 days the original owner can cancel the auction then. 
If the original owner doesn't cancel it before the 7th day the object is remove
from the auction house forever. 

   When an object is auctioned, canceled from auction, bid on, or picked up an
announcement is sent to all those wearing scouters. 

Syntax In Auction House:
 auction (object) (value)
 cancel
 pickup

Syntax Outside Auction House:
 bid (object) (amount)
 bid list
 bid appraise (number)
