COMBINE
--------------
   Combining attacks is a useful ability that any group can accomplish provided
they know the required skills. The benefits to doing this is an increased
power to the attack (usually), increased accuracy (maybe), and various effects
determined mainly by the leading attack (fired by the leader). The more of a
similar attack that have been merged into the combined attack the more of a
bonus the attack will receive. If all the attacks are the same then an extra
bonus will be added on top of that. 

   Combining attacks is a process that required the FOLLOWERS of the group to
first prepare their attacks. When all the group members have their attacks
ready that is when the LEADER should "prepare" his attack. At that time the
attack will be launched for better or worse. 

   Take note that it is @RILLEGAL@n to organize a group combined attack without
working it out ICly through IC channels. There must exist the possibility that
your opponents will figure out what you are doing. No organizing it OOCly. 

