victim and user can't leave while the grapple is in effect. The user gets a
damage bonus. 

   Wrap: This is a grapple only use-able by Majins. They wrap themselves
around the victim and attempt to crush the life out of them. It is like choke
in which the grapple will continue until the victim dies or breaks out, and the
user cannot attack. 

