REGENERATE
----------


   Regeneration is a unique ability to a few races. To those who have
regeneration death can be a rare thing to experience. That is if you have the
life force and ki to regenerate. Depending on your skill in regeneration you
will get more out of the LF and ki you use to regenerate. This will help you
spend less in the long run. For Majins and Bios regenerate has the chance to
save them from death if they are cut in half or lose their head. That is if
they have the ki. All regenerate races have the ability to regenerate their
limbs normally though. 
 
Races with Regenerate
-----------------------
   Majins can survive dying from an attack as long as they have 75% (50% for
Self D) of their LF left. All their LF will be used up and they will slowly
regenerate. During that pariod of time they can not be harmed and when fully
regenerated get their PL restored to their weighted max (LF is still drained to
0 though. )) Bio-Androids can survive dying from an attack as long as they
have 75% (50% for Self D) of their LF left. All their LF will be used up and
they will slowly regenerate. During that pariod of time they can not be harmed
and when fully regenerated get their PL restored to their weighted max (LF is
still drained to 0 though. ))
 
Nameks - Just manual use of regenerate
 
Syntax: regenerate (1-100)
 
See also - help appendages, help limbs
