SHEATH
----------

   Sheaths are objects that can be purchased at certain stores, and are used as
a worn object on the body to store weapons. To store a weapon inside of a
sheath, you must type "put <weapon> sheath". If the weapon is too big, it will
not fit in the sheath. Most sheaths can only hold a single weapon at a time.
To get a weapon from your sheath, type "get <weapon> sheath".
