   Shops come in a variety of shapes, sizes, and dealing in different
categories of objects. While most shops will purchase goods similar to what
they sell (example: buying armor because they also sell armor) the shops to
sell goods at are identified by the "Pawn" moniker. Pawn shops will purchase a
