SKILLS
----------

   Skills is a command that lists the skills you know. These have their own
level and depending on that level will rate their chances of success and how
strong their effects are. Skills can be trained through use once they have
been learned, or through practicing them at an official trainer. As PS is hard
to come by it is more efficient to train through use than to spend PS. PS
should be saved as much as possible for learning new skills. 

   You can limit what the command skills shows you by using it with an
argument. Such as a number to limit skills to showing you the skills you have
that have a level of that number or greater, or a string of letters to show
 skills that have those letters in their name. 

